## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's Prediction feature, which uses AI to segment users based on their likelihood to perform future actions rather than past behaviors. It helps optimize targeting workflows for maximum lift, particularly in communication frequency, dynamic pricing, and content personalization, by building mathematical models that predict user actions.

